Fred Montague https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Montague 0 Fred Montague (1864 – 3 July 1919) was an English film actor of the silent era. He appeared in 59 films between 1912 and 1919. He was born in London and died in Los Angeles, California. Fred_Montague ( 1864 – 3_July_1919 ) was an_English_film_actor of the_silent_era . He appeared in 59_films between 1912_and_1919 .
